    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home! This beauty is in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It drives like a dream and is perfect for everything from daily commutes to fun weekend road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. Drop me a message if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
