    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, premium driving experience. Meticulously cared for, the exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a well-loved car. The interior is a standout feature, with the leather seats remaining firm and free of any significant wear, while all dashboard components and electronic features\u2014from the navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; it starts instantly, idles smoothly, and delivers consistent power through all gears. We have recently performed a comprehensive fluid flush and a brake inspection to ensure it is road-ready. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, comfortable cabin environment that makes it perfect for both daily commutes and long-distance travel.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
