    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a superior balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it features a refined interior and robust mechanical integrity. Ideal for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience, this model has undergone a rigorous professional assessment to ensure its steadfast quality and immediate readiness for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
