    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and she's been incredibly reliable for me. It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great and drives smoothly, this is the one! Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
