    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This example delivers linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the chassis integrity matches its mechanical prowess. Fitted with an upgraded cooling system and Bilstein coilovers for sharpened turn-in and superior damping control. The exterior displays minor road-derived patina, but the drivetrain remains taut and responsive, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
